      "title": "COVID-19: Six deaths, 164 cases reported",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Government Information Department stated that six deaths COVID-19 deaths were reported for Thursday (18).",
        "Four of the deceased were identified as those over the age of 60 years, while the other two were under 30 years of age.",
        "Meanwhile, 164 COVID-19 cases were also reported on Friday (19), increasing the full COVID-19 tally to 668,827.",
        "CIABOC discontinues 2018 MP crossover probe due to \u2018insufficient information\u2019"
      ],
